{"tid":1550752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中共：社會改造 4 步曲","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:28.000Z","uid":264340,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5265b88bb658bc1cdfdd77db0e0dfaa5ecefc512","tid":1550752,"uid":264340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:26:28.000Z","msg":"中共係用仇恨黎治國，呢個係中共體制上必然導致既結果，內蒙新疆西藏已經發生過，希望香港唔好成為第四個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再貼多次共產黨係東歐多國用既社會改造 4 步曲，係 1984 年前蘇聯宣傳部既特工投靠美國後寫，當中好多點係同一般既人性結合左，如果冇受過好好既教育，或主動去抗拒佢地，就會好易被改造<br />\n<br />\n書可以睇呢度：<a href=\"https://archive.org/details/BezmenovLoveLetterToAmerica\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2FBezmenovLoveLetterToAmerica&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=ce8f23ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.org/details/BezmenovLoveLetterToAmerica</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係節錄<br />\n<br />\n第一步：去道德化（包括思想、社會結構、生活的去道德化，維持 20 年）<br />\n- 宗教：政治化<br />\n- 教育；著重相對正確或相對錯誤，令人唔再堅持真相，導致集體主義<br />\n- 媒體：集中報導非重要既議題，轉移視線，忽略真正既議題<br />\n- 法律：只針對有冇程序上守法，而無視法律承載既道德<br />\n- 社會關係：著重無義務既權利，令個體減少責任<br />\n<br />\n第二步：社會動盪（維持 5 年）<br />\n- 有政黨以空頭支票取得權力，承諾工作保障、社會安全，但實則支持共產主義<br />\n- 草根階層參政<br />\n- 政府極度官僚化，由三權分立演變為實則為管治 - 經商 - 勞工三大權力<br />\n- 外交孤立<br />\n<br />\n第三步：危機（維持半年）<br />\n- 權力變天，經濟勢力重新分佈，重點行業國有化<br />\n<br />\n第四步：社會規範化<br />\n- 軍隊進場，強制實施社會主義"},{"pid":"b770b667b31c1f92055e20d1beb45d475643cfc2","tid":1550752,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:28:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c1e10f61bceb959f6d9ae4aaa77b43cf84634ce","tid":1550752,"uid":107138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUq8PfJ.png&h=6ed8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外以下口號可以一記：<br />\n-Free Hong Kong, Democracy now!<br />\n-Fight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong!<br />\n-Five Demands, Not one less!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">練定美國國歌一齊唱K</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=fc3c99ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a>"},{"pid":"497ad0384a94c132442ea9946ba3c216a058441d","tid":1550752,"uid":241106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:28.000Z","msg":"叫佢老母返去發夢"}]}